comments.content: The molecular interactions of different cells in the pancreatic cancer tumor microenvironment (TME). Pancreatic cancer cells have developed various ways of evading and manipulating the immune system, and the TME plays an essential role in this. Various molecular interactions are involved in the interactions between cells in the TME.
